## Customization

```python
bar = ProgressBar(
    total=100,
    desc="Custom",
    width=30,          # Bar width
    fill="â–“",          # Filled character
    empty="â–‘",         # Empty character
    show_percent=True, # Show percentage
    show_count=True,   # Show current/total
    show_eta=True,     # Show time remaining
)
```

